ve two separate identities, one on premise and one in the cloud.", "tokens": [50540, 639, 307, 689, 291, 920, 362, 732, 4994, 24239, 11, 472, 322, 22045, 293, 472, 294, 264, 4588, 13, 50764], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1458205180381661, "compression_ratio": 1.9303135888501741, "no_speech_prob": 0.0011920302640646696}, {"id": 33, "seek": 14216, "start": 150.16, "end": 154.24, "text": " But the key difference between linked identity and synced identity, in sync, there was if", "tokens": [50764, 583, 264, 2141, 2649, 1296, 9408, 6575, 293, 5451, 1232, 6575, 11, 294, 20271, 11, 456, 390, 498, 50968], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1458205180381661, "compression_ratio": 1.9303135888501741, "no_speech_prob": 0.0011920302640646696}, {"id": 34, "seek": 14216, "start": 154.24, "end": 156.8, "text": " a change was made to one, it was synchronized to the other.", "tokens": [50968, 257, 1319, 390, 1027, 281, 472, 11, 309, 390, 19331, 1602, 281, 264, 661, 13, 51096], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1458205180381661, "compression_ratio": 1.9303135888501741, "no_speech_prob": 0.0011920302640646696}, {"id": 35, "seek": 14216, "start": 156.8, "end": 160.74, "text": " In linked, there's a connection to say that these are both accounts that belong to the", "tokens": [51096, 682, 9408, 11, 456, 311, 257, 4984, 281, 584, 300, 613, 366, 1293, 9402, 300, 5784, 281, 264, 51293], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1458205180381661, "compression_ratio": 1.9303135888501741, "no_speech_prob": 0.0011920302640646696}, {"id": 36, "seek": 14216, "start": 160.74, "end": 166.68, "text": " same user, but an update to one does not synchronize automatically, update the other.", "tokens": [51293, 912, 4195, 11, 457, 364, 5623, 281, 472, 775, 406, 19331, 1125, 6772, 11, 5623, 264, 661, 13, 51590], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1458205180381661, "compression_ratio": 1.9303135888501741, "no_speech_prob": 0.0011920302640646696}, {"id": 37, "seek": 14216, "start": 166.68, "